lead_paragraph: The Australian leader said President Trump confirmed that he would carry out an Obama-era deal to resettle in the U.S. migrants held by Australia on two Pacific islands.
snippet: The Australian leader said President Trump confirmed that he would carry out an Obama-era deal to resettle in the U.S. migrants held by Australia on two Pacific islands....

headline.main: Australia Says Trump Will Honor One-Time Deal to Accept Refugees
headline.print_headline: Australia  Says U.S. Will Accept Refugees
